<style>
  .my-button {
    background-color: #3f51b5;
    color: white;
    border: 0;
    padding: 1em;
  }
</style>
<button id="my-button" class="my-button">Greetings!</button>
<script type="module">
  document.getElementById("my-button").addEventListener("click", () => {
    window.dispatchEvent(new CustomEvent('openSnackBar', {detail: {payload: {message: "Welcome!", action: "Got it!"}}}))
  })
</script>
